ou‚Äôre considering canceling your hosting services with us. Your satisfaction means a lot to us, and I‚Äôd love to hear if there‚Äôs anything, whether it‚Äôs pricing, features, or support, that we could improve to better suit your needs. Your feedback is incredibly valuable and helps us enhance our services.\\n\\nIf you still wish to proceed with the cancellation, here are the steps:\\n\\n1. Log in to your Client Area.\\n2. Navigate to Products and Services.\\n3. Select the product you‚Äôd like to cancel.\\n4. Go to the Billing section.\\n5. Choose Cancellation Options and follow the prompts.\\n\\nOnce you‚Äôve submitted the request, let me know, and I‚Äôll ensure everything is handled smoothly. In the meantime, your product will remain active.\\n\\nIf there‚Äôs anything else I can do to make things right or improve your experience, please don‚Äôt hesitate to let me know. I‚Äôd love the opportunity to continue supporting you!\\n\\nWarm regards,\\nDenis\", \"Oct 27th 23:37 PM\\n from IP 94.156.219.172\"]','cmhty86rl0000ooon6j5qix5j','2025-11-13 03:22:37.642','2025-11-13 03:30:49.900','https://admin.worldhost.group/admin/support/inbox/1e509897-3d24-7511-0800-c345e610832d'),('DDF-684-87219__day__2025-11-12','Webcentral','Chris Michael','Issues sending emails','Iwan Setiawan','Email','Awaiting Response','an hour ago\n from IP 43.245.153.52','2025-11-12','[\"I am having issues and having continious issues sending emails I need this fixed urgently\", \"an hour ago\\n from IP 43.245.153.52\"]','[\"Hi there,\\n\\nThank you for contacting our support.\\n\\nUpon checking, it appears that your emails are being sent directly from the cPanel server instead of through your current email service provider, Microsoft 365 (M365). Could you please confirm whether apm-solutions.com.au is configured as the sending email or SMTP address in a website form or application?\\n\\nTo resolve this issue, please update your form or SMTP settings to connect using your M365 email credentials. Thi