8.196.49\", \"escalated: https://teams.microsoft.com/l/message/19:c94a9349f1b940be948302fd2610b65a@thread.tacv2/1762742551287?tenantId=ea8e08e3-9c7a-40c0-95ef-6ec0a852a961&groupId=fc2878a7-ff2a-475b-819a-d58a6e517b96&parentMessageId=1762742551287&teamName=Customer%20Care&channelName=Escalated%20Support&createdTime=1762742551287\\ninfra: https://teams.microsoft.com/l/message/19:4cf00615733349e6b097b554aa902e48@thread.tacv2/1762743874843?tenantId=ea8e08e3-9c7a-40c0-95ef-6ec0a852a961&groupId=1709c7c8-a26b-4b8f-ad25-1f3a842514fd&parentMessageId=1762743874843&teamName=hosting.com&channelName=ask-infra&createdTime=1762743874843\\nlivechat: https://livechat.sgp1.whgi.net/app/accounts/2/conversations/164195\", \"Nov 10th 11:08 AM\\n from IP 202.58.196.49\", \"Hello,\\n\\nI am raising this ticket, as per our live chat conversation, regarding the issue you are experiencing.\\n\\nThe affected domain/service is: Exceed Managed Dedicated Server (server.seniorcarenewsletter.com)\\n\\nDetails identified from the chat investigation: Server intermittently slow and even time out\\n\\nOur team will further investigate the issue and will update you in more detail once it is resolved.\\n\\nPlease feel free to send any additional information that you see fit.\\n\\nKind regards,\\nEgy\", \"Nov 10th 11:08 AM\\n from IP 202.58.196.49\"]','cmhty86rl0000ooon6j5qix5j','2025-11-11 02:30:19.733','2025-11-11 05:11:01.820',NULL),('GWP-888-01885__day__2025-11-13','TMDHosting','Alexander Villforth c/o Odenthal','External Domain Question','Iwan Setiawan','Website','Awaiting Response','5 hours ago\n from IP 77.13.109.135','2025-11-13','[\"Install a SSL sever is not possible since its justt a domain registrar. So i just set an A Server in the DNS there ?\", \"38 minutes ago\\n from IP 89.12.189.249\", \"the domain is wikiparse.com and the url would be axchapman.com/wikiparse.php\\n\\n(the file.php was just an example)\", \"4 hours ago\\n from IP 77.13.109.135\", \"Hello TMD Hosting Team,\\n\\nI have an external domain that I‚Äôm redirecting to my hosting account, and I would like it to forward to axchapman.com/file.php.\\n\\nWhen I use a frame redirect, the domain displays as http, even though the server here uses https.\\n\\nIs there a method on the DNS side of the external domain that would allow the redirect to retain and display https?\\n\\nI know this isn‚Äôt strictly product-related, but any guidance or tips would be nice\\n\\nGreetings, A.Villforth\", \"5 hours ago\\n from IP 77.13.109.135\"]','[\"Hi there,\\n\\nThank you for your response.\\n\\nIf your domain currently doesn‚Äôt have any records, or if you‚Äôve just purchased the domain, you can point it to your cPanel in either of the following ways:\\n\\nUpdate the A records in your DNS manager to: 65.60.5.219\\nor\\nUpdate your domain name servers to:\\nns1.c05.tmdcloud.com\\nns2.c05.tmdcloud.com\\n\\nOnce updated, you can add the domain to your cPanel. This will ensure the domain is correctly pointed to your hosting. After DNS propagation, you should be able to set up a redirection, SSL, or configure an iframe as needed.\\n\\nRegards,\\nIwan\", \"a few seconds ago\\n from IP 202.58.196.49\", \"This ticket was unassigned due to inactivity. Here is a quick summary of what has happened so far:\\n\\nThe customer, A. Villforth, inquired about redirecting their external domain (wikiparse.com) to axchapman.com/file.php while retaining HTTPS. The agent explained that since wikiparse.com is only a domain registrar, they should set an A record in the DNS. The agent also noted that for HTTPS to display correctly, an SSL certificate must be installed on the external domain. The customer confirmed they set an A record but sought further clarification on the process.\", \"30 minutes ago\\n from IP 192.250.239.172\", \"Hi there,\\n\\nThank you for the details.\\n\\nA frame/iframe redirect will always load the target URL inside the frame, and since the frame URL itself belongs to the external domain http://wikiparse.com/, it will show as HTTP unless the external domain has its own valid SSL certificate installed.\\n\\nTo have your external domain display HTTPS while forwarding to axchapman.com/file.php, you would need to:\\n\\nPoint the external domain directly to your hosting account using A records or use it as an addon/parked domain, and\\n\\nInstall an SSL certificate for that external domain on the server.\\n\\nOnce the domain loads directly from the server and has SSL installed, it will automatically show HTTPS.\\n\\nRegards,\\nIwan\", \"3 hours ago\\n from IP 202.58.196.49\", \"Hi there,\\n\\nThank you for the details.\\n\\nTo assist you further, could you please let us know the name of the external domain you are trying to redirect to axchapman.com/file.php? Once we have the domain, we can check its current DNS setup and advise on the best method to ensure the redirect works properly over HTTPS.\\n\\nPlease also note that the URL axchapman.com/file.php is currently returning a 404 error. Once we have the external domain name, we can review the setup and help ensure the destination URL is accessible as well.\\n\\nLooking forward to your reply.\\n\\nRegards,\\nIwan\", \"5 hours ago\\n from IP 202.58.196.49\"]','cmhty86rl0000ooon6j5qix5j','2025-11-13 07:11:15.044','2025-11-13 07:11:33.649','https://admin.worldhost.group/admin/support/inbox/52d137e0-8d24-1031-2739-f3495163789e'),('HVL-291-03308__day__2025-11-13','hosting.com','zach lee','Re: Information Required to Complete Your Order','Iwan Setiawan','Product','Awaiting Response','40 minutes ago\n via \nemail','2025-11-13','[\"I\'m sorry, I\'m trying to migrate \\\"vigormedia.tw\\\",\\nbut the invoice details are: 1x Managed Linux VPS M - \\\"vigormedia.se\\\".\\nWill this cause a migration error?\\n\\n\\nZach Lee/ Êùé‰Ω≥Ëä≥\\nR&D Dept.\\nZoeTek Technology Co., Ltd. (ÂãïÂøÉÈÜ´ÈõªËÇ°‰ªΩÊúâÈôêÂÖ¨Âè∏)\\n\\n112 Âè∞ÂåóÂ∏ÇÂåóÊäïÂçÄÁ´ãÂæ∑Ë∑Ø120Â∑∑18Ëôü3Ê®ì\\n\\nTel:+886-2-28946661\\nFax:+886-2-28923222\\n\\nMobile:+886-958504589\