ite is not protected‚Äô message. Regards, Jill\\n\\n\\n\\nFrom: Webcentral Support <support@webcentral.au>\\nSent: Tuesday, November 11, 2025 3:25 PM\\nTo: Jill ILIFFE <jilliliffe@gmail.com>\\nSubject: New Support Ticket Message - WCG-KMA-945-50017 - SSL installation on domain unitsplan439.org\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n<https://theconsole.webcentral.au/login>\\n\\n\\n\\nHi Jill,\\n\\nThis is a reply to ticket WCG-KMA-945-50017 from Okbar G..\\n\\nThe ticket subject is SSL installation on domain unitsplan439.org\\n\\n---\\nHello there Jill,\\n\\nThankk you for your update.\\n\\nI can confirm that your domain unitsplan439.org currently does not have an SSL certificate installed. The installation error occurred due to a rate limit, as multiple failed SSL installation attempts triggered a restriction.\\n\\nTo resolve this, we‚Äôll need to wait for the SSL installation rate limit to reset, which may take around 12 hours, provided no further installation attempts are made during that time.\\n\\nAlternatively, if you prefer, I can proceed to install a free SSL certificate from another trusted provider outside of cPanel, which will secure your domain without any additional cost.\\n\\nPlease let me know how you‚Äôd like to proceed, and I‚Äôll take care of it for you.\\n\\nThank you for your patience and understanding.\\n\\nWarm Regards,\\n\\nOkbar G\\nSupport Team\\n---\\n\\nIf you wish to reply to this email please keep the subject line intact.\\n\\nKind regards,\\nWebcentral\\n\\n\\n\\nYou received this email because you are subscribed to Support notifications. Click here <https://theconsole.webcentral.au/preferences?username=jilliliffe%40gmail.com&token=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzUxMiJ9.eyJleHAiOjE3NjU0MjcwOTEuMTcyOTk0LCJzdWIiOiIxNTQzMjU2IiwidXNlcl90eXBlIjoiY2xpZW50Iiwic2NvcGVzIjpbIm1hbmFnZV9ub3RpZmljYXRpb25fc3VicyJdLCJvcmdfaWQiOjI5fQ.uPivVdUVKbQJDDPqWm0vr1G_zQba9smcENcfjJrhzvHf_ltrORQu1SkO7JkyYcQAl_kHoVE5CirUebUv2oXcaQ> to manage your subscription preferences.\", \"3 hours ago