atly appreciated so that we can proceed smoothly.\\n\\n\\n\\nKind regards,\\n\\nDurga\\n\\n\\n\\nFrom: FastComet Support <support@fastcomet.com>\\nSent: 10 November 2025 19:06\\nTo: Durga Muktan <maildurga@gmail.com>\\nSubject: New Support Ticket Message - WGL-806-50746 - Need to change the main domain name\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n<https://cloud.fastcomet.com/login>\\n\\n\\n\\nYou have received a new reply to your support ticket from Usman H.\\n\\nTicket Reference: WGL-806-50746 <https://cloud.fastcomet.com/support/tickets/983e2306-e754-00e3-8d87-b14981d210d7?m_id=0d1639e2-37d4-3e50-69d8-f64610589e57>\\n\\nTicket Subject: Need to change the main domain name\\n\\n---\\n\\nMessage: Hello Durga,\\n\\nThank you for contacting support. I\'m happy to assist you.\\n\\nWe can change the primary domain name from laser-travel.com.np to laser-travel.com. However, please note and confirm the following before we proceed.\\n\\n1- All email and FTP accounts linked with laser-travel.com.np will be lost. They will change from @laser-travel.com.np to @laser-travel.com\\n2- Please make sure laser-travel.com does not exist in your cPanel as an addon or domain alias else it can not be made the primary domain name of your hosting account.\\n3- Once laser-travel.com is made the main domain, it will load its content from the public_html folder. You may need to consult a developer to make laser-travel.com work with old content.\\n4- If you have a paid SSL, the SSL vendor will not rename it, so you may have to purchase a new paid SSL for similar coverage. Domains with free SSLs will have a new SSL issued automatically within a few hours of DNS propagation of the new domain name.\\n\\nYour username and password will not be affected by this change. Your site may be unavailable for up to 24 hours during this process.\\n\\nRemember, our scope of services is limited to the server level only. Hence, any changes required after changing the primary domain will need to be handled from your side.\\n\\nUsman 